  "title": "The excellence of asking for Allah's blessings upon the Prophet PBUH",
  "source": "Hisn al-Muslim 220",
  "arabic": "وَقَالَ صلى الله عليه وسلم لاَ تَجْعَلُوا قَبْرِي عِيداً وَصَلُّوا عَلَيَّ فَإِنَّ صَلاَتَكُم تَبْلُغُنِي حَيْثُ كُنْتُمْ",
  "meaning": "He (PBUH) also said: ‘Do not take my grave as a place of habitual ceremony. Send prayers upon me, for verily your prayers reach me wherever you are.",
